==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sertularian
<hw>Ser`tu*la"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any species of Sertularia, or of <fam>Sertularidae</fam>, a family
of hydroids having branched chitinous stems and simple sessile
hydrothecae. Also used adjectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Serum</ent>⟦br⟧
